libkiwix
------------------------------------------
The Libkiwix provides the Kiwix software suite core. It contains the code
shared by all Kiwix ports (Windows, GNU/Linux, macOS, Android, iOS, ...).

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.6-1
  libcurl-devel-8.0.1-1
  libcurl4-8.0.1-1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libicu-devel-72.1-1
  libicu72-72.1-1
  libkiwix-devel-12.0.0-1bl3
  libkiwix12-12.0.0-1bl3
  libmicrohttpd-devel-0.9.76-1bl1
  libmicrohttpd12-0.9.76-1bl1
  libpugixml1-1.9-1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  libxapian-devel-1.4.5-1
  libxapian30-1.4.5-1
  libzim-devel-8.1.1-1bl1
  libzim8-8.1.1-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.9.4-1
  python39-3.9.16-1
  zlib0-1.2.13-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.40-1
  cygport-0.36.1-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libcurl-devel-8.0.1-1
  libicu-devel-72.1-1
  libmicrohttpd-devel-0.9.76-1bl1
  libpugixml-devel-1.9-1
  libxapian-devel-1.4.5-1
  libzim-devel-8.1.1-1bl1
  meson-0.63.3-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1
  zlib-devel-1.2.13-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/kiwix/libkiwix

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/kiwix/libkiwix/archive/refs/tags/12.0.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libkiwix-12.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libkiwix-12.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libkiwix-12.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkiwix-12.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkiwix12-12.0.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libkiwix-devel-12.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libkiwix)
  /usr/bin/kiwix-compile-i18n
  /usr/bin/kiwix-compile-resources
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libkiwix.README
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libkiwix/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-compile-i18n.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-compile-resources.1.gz

(libkiwix12)
  /usr/bin/cygkiwix-12.dll

(libkiwix-devel)
  /usr/include/kiwix/book.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/bookmark.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/common.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/downloader.h
  /usr/include/kiwix/kiwix_config.h
